This is the canonical word count example for Hadoop. A copy of The Iliad is
provided for testing.

http://slacr.evergreen.edu/wiki/index.php/MapReduce_Counting_Words

Compiling:
javac -cp /usr/share/hadoop/hadoop-core* -d classfiles WordCount.java
jar cf wordcount.jar -C classfiles/ .

Running:
(As a hadoop user)
(First set up your input)
hadoop fs -mkdir wordcount wordcount/input
hadoop fs -put iliad_pope.txt wordcount/input
(Now run it)
hadoop jar wordcount.jar org.slacr.WordCount wordcount/input wordcount/output
